explains: adv. 象征性地；象征意义地

sentences.en: Each circle symbolically represents the whole of humanity.
sentences.cn: 每个圆圈都象征性地代表全人类。

sentences.en: It was a simple enough gesture, but symbolically important.
sentences.cn: 这虽是个再简单不过的手势，但却有着重要的象征意义。

sentences.en: Symbolically significant donations are pouring in too.
sentences.cn: 象征性意义重大的捐助也在跟进。
